channel.title: Clean mudclient
channel.description:
Hey all, I was wondering if there were releases somewhere of mudclients that have EVERYTHING included. When I say everything I mean decompiled source and the correct cache. For some reason, I can't find any public releases that contains both of these..
Come to think of it - there was a mudclient 176 (or something) that was released a month or two ago... but im looking for something newer.
